OL,7,FAge Cymru say in their 2024 annual
OL,8,Fsurvey of over 1300 older people
OL,9,Facross Wales, almost half of older
OL,10,Fpeople found cost of living to be a
OL,11,Fchallenge over the last 12 months, and
OL,12,Fover half of older people had issues
OL,13,Fwith their physical health.
OL,15,FThey say this will only worsen with
OL,16,Fcuts to this vital financial support
OL,17,Fduring the winter months.
