OL,7,FAn Age UK petition to reverse the
OL,8,Fchanges to the winter fuel allowance
OL,9,Fhas more than 470,000 signatures - Age
OL,10,FCymru say 18,000 of those are people
OL,11,Fin Wales.
OL,13,FThe Chancellor has defended the move
OL,14,Fto scrap the payments for some
OL,15,Fpensioners insisting it will be offset
OL,16,Fby increases by pensions and lower
OL,17,Fenergy prices this winter compared to
OL,18,Flast year.
